short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A full-featured front end for George with various qualify-of-life features and workflow improvements.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
After installing, visit Ask George at https://www.student.cs.uwaterloo.ca/~se212/george/ask-george/.

### Features

* Auto-complete

* File management for assignments and homeworks (auto-fetching, saving, downloading)

* Verification by George (with distinct indicators for different types of feedback)
